    "\n",
    "1. **Claude Code CLI** installed and working\n",
    "2. **Python 3.11+** installed\n",
    "3. **Git** installed and configured\n",
    "4. A text editor for viewing/editing JSON files\n",
    "5. Basic command line knowledge\n",
    "\n",
    "### Check Prerequisites"
